  "DescIdentified": {
    "type": "cexolocstring",
    "value": {
      "0": "Priests of Lathander created this weapon to fight the hordes of undead created by Myrkulites across Faerun. The massive blade has changed hands frequently as it is needed in different regions at different times. Somewhere along its history, the notched sword fell into the hands of a Zhentilar soldier who was, not surprisingly, unwilling to return it to the church of Lathander. The heretofore nameless soldier used the blade to defend himself against rival priests of Bane and wizards in the Zhentarim until he was killed in battle by a triad of wizards. They sold the weapon to the highest bidder a month after his death.\n"
    }
